com.guardtime.ksi.publication

Class PublicationData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guardtime.ksi.tlv.TLVStructure
      • com.guardtime.ksi.publication.PublicationData

  • public class PublicationData
extends TLVStructure
    Record of publication data, it is a pair consisting of the publication time and publication hash. It's TLV encoded form is used for signing and verifying authentication records.

    • Constructor Detail

      • PublicationData

        public PublicationData(TLVElement rootElement)
                throws KSIException
        Creates a new publication data from TLV element. Parses publication time and publication hash elements from TLVElement. TLV element must contain publication hash and publication time elements.
        Parameters:
        rootElement - - TLV element to parse to publication data. not null.
        Throws:
        KSIException

      • PublicationData

        public PublicationData(String publicationString)
                throws KSIException
        Create a publication object from a publication string. A publication string is a base-32 encoded value that is meant published to print media as human readable text or a QR code.
        Parameters:
        publicationString - publication in string format. not null.
        Throws:
        KSIException
